data.description:
*** $5,000 Seller's Concession towards Closing Costs ***  Welcome to this charming gem nestled in the highly sought-after Wolf Creek Run community! This adorable home boasts an array of features that will surely capture your heart.

Discover convenience with a main-floor bedroom and a 3/4 bath, making it perfect for guests or family members seeking one-level living. An inviting open floor plan awaits, seamlessly connecting the family room, dining room, and kitchen. It's an ideal setup for gatherings and everyday living.

Head upstairs to find three generously sized bedrooms, offering comfort and privacy for everyone in the family.
The walk-in laundry room adds a touch of luxury to your daily routines. A well-appointed bathroom ensures mornings run smoothly.

Greet your neighbors with a friendly wave from your covered front porch, creating a welcoming atmosphere.
The poured walkway leading to the front door not only adds curb appeal but also enhances accessibility for your guests.
Entertain effortlessly in your backyard haven, complete with a spacious patio, a convenient poured walkway to the garage, a sprinkler system for lush landscaping, and secure fencing. Park your vehicles in the 2-car garage, and there's additional space with a gravel driveway in the rear of the home for extra parking options.

Wolf Creek Run is more than just a neighborhood; it's a lifestyle. Enjoy endless fun at the community pool and park, perfect for those sunny summer days. Take leisurely strolls on the nearby walking trails, connecting you with nature and your neighbors.
Commuting is a breeze with quick access to major highways, making your daily journeys hassle-free.

Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this gorgeous home your own! It's a gem of a home in an exceptional community. Schedule a showing today and step into your dream home.
